asthmatic /æsˈmætɪk/

1. N-COUNT People who suffer from asthma are sometimes referred to as asthmatics . 哮喘病人 

例： I have been an asthmatic from childhood and was never able to play any sports. 我从小就是个哮喘病人，从来不能参加任何体育运动。 

2. ADJ Asthmatic is also an adjective. 患哮喘病的 

例： One child in ten is asthmatic. 每10个孩子中有1个是患哮喘病的。 

3. ADJ Asthmatic means relating to asthma. 哮喘性的 [ADJ n] 

例： ...asthmatic breathing. …哮喘性呼吸。

